title: Why cannot the M635 access the Internetï¼Ÿ
answer:
By default, the M635 can access the Internet.  
If it cannot access the Internet, do the following:  
1. Check whether the call function can be used.  
2. Check whether you have subscribed to the data service.  
3. Select MetroWEB ->Options -> Settings -> Reset to reset the browser.  
If the phone still cannot access the Internet, restore the phone to factory settings or contact the local operator.
